node.text:
I made these lil self defense alarms, this is Wisp. 🍄

He makes an extremely loud signal to help you in dangerous situations. You can attach him to your keychain. He has been in the works since last year and 1/3 character models I am coming out with! I am expanding my catalogue of custom self defense weapons unique to Alyssa D. Silos art. 😌 this is just the beginning friends!
